Lana's route means choose the topmost menu items when asked a question.
This walkthrough is for Lana's route

Day 1:
    Go to the kitchen and click on the counter top to do the dishes.
    Go outside on the porch (where you can see next door) and sweep it.
    Go to the living room and click on Lana.
    Menu - Borrow Money.
    Go to the mailbox and buy a drone.
    Buy 2 flowers and 2 bears.
    Go to the living room and click on Lana.
    Give Lana the 2 flowers and two bears.
    Menu - What are you doing up so early?
    Menu - For you, absolutely (LR) / Of course! That's what friends are for. (RR)
    Menu - Nothing else.
    Go to the backyard where Lana does yoga and click on the fence area.
    Menu - Hop the fence
    Click on the steps.
    Go to Lana's bedroom.
    Menu - Me, after seeing you. (LR) / Wow, you look amazing! (RR)
    Menu - He's not worth the trouble. (LR / You're worth it. (RR)
    Go to the front of the house (Step off the porch).
    Click on the computer and click on the e-mail button.
    Go to the guest room
    Go to Lana's bedroom.
    Go to the guest room and sleep.
    End of day 1
    
Day 2:
    Menu - I love it, you look amazing (LR) / Not bad at all (RR)
    If you don't have a camera, go to the mailbox and get one with the money Lana gives you then go to here bedroom.
    Take the pictures using the camera wheel.
    Go to the backyard where Lana does yoga and click on the fence area.
    Menu - Fly my drone
    Click on the computer and click on the e-mail button.
    Go in the Living room and click on the TV.
    Go to the kitchen and click on the counter top to do the dishes.
    Go to Lana's bedroom.
    Go to the theater room.    
    Go to the guest room and sleep.
    End of day 1
    
